Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.00,0:00:12.00,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}翻譯：ひまひま 小約 飯糰粽子   後期：sslish
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.22,0:02:02.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.40,0:02:04.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.53,0:02:06.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊…週一就是沒幹勁
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.98,0:02:12.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.76,0:02:28.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,期待已久的這一天終於來了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.53,0:02:31.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾往來多次的上學路
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.18,0:02:35.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為現在立場的不同總有種新鮮的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.80,0:02:41.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你們幾個
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.36,0:02:46.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經成了高中生了 就別隨意亂扔垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.93,0:02:53.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.24,0:03:03.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長瀨純 21歲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.52,0:03:04.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從今天起是個老師
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.37,0:03:07.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲 教育實習生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.70,0:03:10.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二階堂前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.84,0:03:12.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不見
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.31,0:03:16.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是老樣子 無憂無慮的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.99,0:03:21.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣 今年我們學校的畢業生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.72,0:03:24.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為實習生回到了這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.39,0:03:25.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然只有兩週的時間
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.28,0:03:28.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也請大家互相關照
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.17,0:03:32.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來一個個打一聲招呼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.32,0:03:36.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是鳴澤教育大學4年級的長瀨純
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.91,0:03:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請大家多多~指教了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.29,0:03:42.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔 真好真好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.04,0:03:46.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們學校的畢業生裡也有這樣的美女呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.48,0:03:50.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尊敬的人是巨漢鶴馬
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.85,0:03:53.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鶴馬？那個摔角選手？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.90,0:03:55.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真令人懷念
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.97,0:03:58.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這孩子多大了啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.59,0:04:03.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳還在喜歡職業摔角嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.00,0:04:04.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.97,0:04:06.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還是過去的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.26,0:04:07.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.66,0:04:12.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摔角正是追逐夢想與希望以及理想和強大的運動
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.59,0:04:15.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教育不也正是如此嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.37,0:04:22.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想成為擁有崇高理想的教師
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.85,0:04:26.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳喜歡把「喔」說成「喔~」就是因為喜歡鶴馬嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.57,0:04:32.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有這樣嗎？真討厭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.20,0:04:37.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過意外的有朝氣 那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.10,0:04:39.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意外是什麼意思啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.95,0:04:43.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我從以前開始有朝氣就是我唯一的可取之處啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.98,0:04:49.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣 我的後輩來這裡做教育實習
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.67,0:04:52.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這段時間由她擔任副班主任
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.49,0:04:53.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼時候的後輩呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.31,0:04:55.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.92,0:05:01.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家看起來都是好孩子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.59,0:05:14.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 自我介紹
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.71,0:05:20.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫長瀨純 請多多~指教！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.10,0:05:26.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尊敬的人是巨漢鶴馬
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.58,0:05:34.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 開始上課了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.14,0:05:36.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一節是我的課
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.05,0:05:38.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳到後面去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.00,0:05:39.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.31,0:05:51.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打開第13頁
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.78,0:05:55.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}夏目漱石「從此以後」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.00,0:05:55.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔 上次講到哪兒了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.28,0:06:03.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這部作品的主角叫做高等遊民
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.34,0:06:06.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他依靠著父兄的援助生活著
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.57,0:06:09.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說和家裡蹲差不多的那種
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.03,0:06:14.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼誰都沒有注意到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.17,0:06:17.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明有個人在上課時間玩遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.49,0:06:22.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是只有我才能看到的地縛靈吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.79,0:06:30.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不太可能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.63,0:06:36.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 那是桂木
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.25,0:06:39.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桂木…同學？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.99,0:06:45.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔…怎麼說呢 不用管他
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.38,0:06:47.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用管他？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.07,0:06:50.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種傢伙不用理他
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.89,0:06:51.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這怎麼行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.55,0:06:56.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是玩遊戲而已 稍微讓他注意一下不就好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.22,0:07:00.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說…讓他注意會…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.96,0:07:04.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺人滅口？！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.22,0:07:09.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣還好 總之別理他
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.56,0:07:12.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙連游泳的時候都在玩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.42,0:07:13.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是怪物啊 受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.09,0:07:16.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有完沒完！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.82,0:07:19.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是叫你別玩了嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.00,0:07:26.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滅口魔術師？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.88,0:07:29.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是如果老這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.29,0:07:31.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,課程不就完全聽不進去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.20,0:07:33.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.33,0:07:37.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種事情早就提醒過他了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.93,0:07:41.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這樣上課怎麼可能聽得進去！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.34,0:07:42.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You understand？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.48,0:07:47.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只要能兼顧學業就行了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.27,0:07:48.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.40,0:07:50.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.97,0:07:52.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,考試能拿滿分嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.28,0:07:56.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.64,0:08:00.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從此之後就總是拿滿分
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.37,0:08:04.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 總有一天要給那傢伙一個下馬威
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.21,0:08:08.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在的問題少年…真是複雜難懂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.57,0:08:11.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他也對我說過「妳的課實在太無聊了」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.00,0:08:13.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對他火大了 所以懶得管他
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.46,0:08:23.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為火大所以就放任不管
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.94,0:08:27.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不等於老師拿給學生沒轍了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.11,0:08:33.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該提醒一下他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.45,0:08:40.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我充其量也就是個實習老師
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.72,0:08:58.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對 這和是不是實習老師沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.28,0:09:01.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要好好教~育教育他
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.01,0:09:09.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能行的 能行的 能行的！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.99,0:09:13.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那位是B班的實習老師啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.95,0:09:14.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.13,0:09:25.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桂木同…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.28,0:09:42.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桂…桂木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.36,0:09:48.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩遊戲雖然也可以 不過還是多和朋友一起玩玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.19,0:09:59.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.59,0:10:12.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.03,0:10:16.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.45,0:10:23.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嚇…嚇我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.29,0:10:30.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子的眼神 是真的對現實不抱有任何期待
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.31,0:10:33.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猶如從異世界注視著這個世界的眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.49,0:10:38.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那雙眼睛把所有的老師都打倒了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.75,0:10:41.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是一般的問題少年
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.78,0:10:46.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為感覺他是那麼的孤獨
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.04,0:10:50.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 他是孤獨 是寂寞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.48,0:10:53.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他也不是為了玩遊戲而玩遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.20,0:10:56.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我必須拯救他
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.36,0:10:59.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巨漢鶴馬也說過
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.49,0:11:02.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人生就是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.10,0:11:05.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人生就是 挑戰
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.25,0:11:08.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要讓那孩子回到正軌
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.00,0:11:12.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我 作為老師的第一份工作
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.61,0:11:16.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 我要貫徹我的理想
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.44,0:11:18.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次一定要
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.48,0:11:42.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 剛才那是？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.00,0:11:45.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 第五節課了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.19,0:11:49.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要~趕快 要~趕快
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.95,0:11:54.99,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}FLAG9.0 「2年B班 長瀨老師」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.58,0:12:01.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呀 我們太走運了 聽說隔壁班是男實習老師呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.70,0:12:05.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 在這個班真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.88,0:12:09.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實習生 真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.44,0:12:11.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有股絕妙的香味
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.83,0:12:13.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像是姐姐那種角色
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.51,0:12:17.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可要不客氣了 兩週內和她增加感情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.03,0:12:22.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傻瓜 就你們 對方是不可能搭理你們的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.07,0:12:24.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去照照鏡子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.45,0:12:25.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.23,0:12:30.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家情緒高漲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.75,0:12:35.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教育實習生們真的是富有激情的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.32,0:12:39.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 就那種半吊子的參數 到底哪裡好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.81,0:12:41.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教師的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.68,0:12:46.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}現在正在打分 能不能先不要打擾我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.14,0:12:46.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那種攻略起來很麻煩又收效甚微的類型
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.17,0:12:51.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掛著「教師」的頭銜到底哪裡有魅力了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.36,0:12:52.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家太奇怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.80,0:12:56.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實習教師這種角色 只有是玩家本身時才有存在價值
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.02,0:12:58.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾露西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.58,0:13:05.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 打鈴了 該上課啦 學習去囉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.94,0:13:13.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實習的第二天 今天也得好好幹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.26,0:13:21.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桂木同學 我得為那孩子做些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.59,0:13:26.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come here
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.27,0:13:33.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一堂課是 英語課
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.73,0:13:35.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Say good day
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.22,0:13:37.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good day！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.82,0:13:40.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good day Mr.兒玉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.41,0:13:46.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早…早安 今天也請多多關照了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.14,0:13:51.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安 長瀨老師！！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.35,0:13:56.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 開始上課
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.05,0:13:59.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老…老師嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.69,0:14:05.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不能辜負他們的期望
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.58,0:14:09.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定要成為一位好老師
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.24,0:14:26.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰 是誰把鬧鐘弄響了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.68,0:14:29.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody has 手機
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.41,0:14:31.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對…對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.55,0:14:33.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳至少也用英語給我道歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.05,0:14:35.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Say sorry
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.80,0:14:37.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,S…Sorry
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.17,0:14:40.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說刮鬍刀（此處發音和刮鬍刀一樣）
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.80,0:14:42.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剃鬚刀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.63,0:14:44.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Say 草履蟲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.10,0:14:46.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,草履蟲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.31,0:14:54.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 今天真是碰上倒楣透頂的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.65,0:14:56.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是 關於她的情報呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.98,0:14:58.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.94,0:15:03.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長瀨純 21歲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.72,0:15:05.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴澤師範四年級生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.26,0:15:11.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡的東西是職業摔角 籃球 其他的運動都很喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.93,0:15:13.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概就是這些
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.92,0:15:19.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近沒碰到什麼遊魂 我還鬆了口氣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.41,0:15:21.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天明明還沒有反應的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.83,0:15:26.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許是剛剛進去的也說不定
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.31,0:15:37.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在的話 遊魂的等級還很低 趕快抓住他吧 神大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.58,0:15:39.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 我要回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.23,0:15:45.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 為什麼要回去了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.11,0:15:48.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神大人你欺負人家
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.41,0:15:51.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次都和我唱反調
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.79,0:15:52.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜點
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.23,0:15:55.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在隨隨便便地接近她是很危險的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.23,0:15:59.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是為什麼呀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.88,0:16:03.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我告訴妳一句名言吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.48,0:16:08.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對老師的愛通常是沒有未來的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.86,0:16:16.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教師在GALGAME的理論中是最花時間的職業之一
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.97,0:16:17.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳知道是為什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.58,0:16:20.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是為什麼呀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.22,0:16:23.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是因為她們的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.29,0:16:25.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是為了要和學生們變得親密啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.85,0:16:28.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果只是變親密的話是很簡單的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.25,0:16:32.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 從這之後就開始舉步維艱了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.23,0:16:35.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不在某個點上將立場對等的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.56,0:16:41.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且將曾經牢固的親密關係變為其他形式發展需要巨大的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.29,0:16:47.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以攻略教師是非常需要時間和事件的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.68,0:16:49.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在需要的是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.20,0:16:52.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在對等關係下的開局
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.70,0:16:56.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果成為了她的學生 就無法在短期內解決
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.15,0:17:01.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此 我不會在學校裡再見她了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.57,0:17:03.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那我該怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.59,0:17:07.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用羽衣做一個我的替身幫我上課
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.65,0:17:09.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這段時間裡我去擬定一下計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.71,0:17:10.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.21,0:17:17.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要去哪裡 桂木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.07,0:17:24.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒有…下課哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.74,0:17:28.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼是對方先攻過來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.32,0:17:34.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然中途蹺課 看來他覺得學校相當地無聊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.59,0:17:44.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桂木同學 鏘~
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.63,0:17:48.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要和老師一起吃午飯嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.14,0:17:51.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.06,0:17:54.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.40,0:17:56.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在學校裡發生事件是不行的 快停止
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.35,0:17:59.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.68,0:18:04.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 桂木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.65,0:18:07.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起吃吧~
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.64,0:18:12.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.95,0:18:15.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會讓你逃走的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.30,0:18:19.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定要告訴你學校的有趣之處
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.68,0:18:28.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛痛痛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.12,0:18:35.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱…抱歉啊 你沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.82,0:18:37.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒…沒事…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.83,0:18:44.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我好像有點感冒了 所以想早點回去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.17,0:18:46.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感冒？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.79,0:18:52.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起來很健康啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.53,0:18:59.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係 沒有發燒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.39,0:19:04.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧 再稍微努力一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.25,0:19:07.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別…別碰我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.27,0:19:14.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個蛋炒麵麵包真的很好吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.56,0:19:19.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很久以前也參加過這個蛋炒麵麵包的爭奪大戰哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.18,0:19:23.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是現在竟然可以走後門買到哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.07,0:19:25.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當老師真是厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.64,0:19:29.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會盯上我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.34,0:19:32.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做了什麼糟糕的事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.90,0:19:36.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之不能和她說話 不面對她
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.12,0:19:38.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能提供給她情報
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.58,0:19:44.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.37,0:19:46.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然要他說話…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.95,0:19:51.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 我給你看個好東西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.41,0:19:55.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 快看快看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.22,0:19:59.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 巨漢鶴馬
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.75,0:20:01.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史上最強的摔角手哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.23,0:20:03.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得他如果還活著的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.31,0:20:05.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是現在一定也很厲害哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.73,0:20:11.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師我啊 最喜歡職業摔角了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.14,0:20:15.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然現在綜合格鬥技比較受歡迎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.12,0:20:19.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,格鬥技是追逐著現實中的強大
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.86,0:20:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是職業摔角是追逐著理想中的強大哦 很帥吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.66,0:20:27.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起現實更傾向於理想嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.08,0:20:31.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 桂木同學有反應了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.06,0:20:33.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是鶴馬先生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.27,0:20:39.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了 居然做出了回應
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.52,0:20:48.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桂木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.37,0:20:54.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨時都可以來和我聊天哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.90,0:20:57.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為老師會幫助你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.65,0:21:06.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒誒 已經過招過了嗎 和長瀨老師
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.73,0:21:10.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神大人真是建立親密關係的天才呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.14,0:21:12.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開什麼玩笑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.31,0:21:17.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼啊 為什麼那傢伙會衝著我來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.46,0:21:20.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是擔心你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.67,0:21:22.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為神大人是問題少年啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.33,0:21:28.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我哪裡是問題少年了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.49,0:21:31.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點自覺都沒有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.80,0:21:37.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 如此一來我就進入她的學生範疇裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.99,0:21:40.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全地進入了教師路線啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.60,0:21:43.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是最想避開的展開啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.04,0:21:45.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.51,0:21:48.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結局就會很遙遠
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.96,0:23:34.80,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}FLAG 10.0 校園☆戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.48,0:23:22.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖誕節 情人節 生日以及暑假
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.53,0:23:25.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遊戲中的全年活動唰唰唰地進行著非常的便利
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.63,0:23:26.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而與此相比現實的話
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.10,0:23:29.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要過一年的話起碼要花365天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.90,0:23:30.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多麼沒效率啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.12,0:23:32.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現實太不努力了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.51,0:23:34.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗚…加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.13,0:01:56.33,logo,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(800,400)}{\pos(596,352)}雪酷字幕组
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.04,0:00:33.01,OPen1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}I don't wanna let the chance slip away
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.04,0:00:33.01,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}我不願讓機會溜走
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.14,0:00:36.26,OPen1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Why is my freedom taken away?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.14,0:00:36.26,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}為什麼要剝奪我的自由
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.42,0:00:38.90,OPen1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Reason as against emotion
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.42,0:00:38.90,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}與感性不同 理性更讓我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.90,0:00:43.73,OPen1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}I've gotta deal with extreme frustration
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.90,0:00:43.73,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}必須跨越這挫敗感
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.90,0:00:47.23,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}All my efforts will never be in vain
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.90,0:00:47.23,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}所有努力將不會是徒勞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.23,0:00:50.30,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Endless desire,like a haunting refrain
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.23,0:00:50.30,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}無盡的慾望 在心中不斷反復
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.33,0:00:53.61,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Such a pain,the ideal versus the real
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.33,0:00:53.61,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}夾在理想與現實間的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.61,0:00:56.14,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}There is a way to change the world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.61,0:00:56.14,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}一定有一種可以改變世界的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.17,0:00:57.71,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Just count on me
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.17,0:00:57.71,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}是的 交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.74,0:01:01.01,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}So what if I sing off-key,who cares
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.74,0:01:01.01,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}我歌唱得走調又如何
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.09,0:01:03.09,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Not good at drawing,no big deal
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.09,0:01:03.09,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}手繪不佳也無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.09,0:01:07.85,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Let me go for my one true belief
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.09,0:01:07.85,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}我只會為了追尋那唯一的信念而行動
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.93,0:01:09.50,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}克服我自己
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.93,0:01:09.50,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Overcome yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.93,0:01:09.50,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}克服你自己
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.93,0:01:09.50,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Overcome myself
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.69,0:01:12.84,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}“A whole new world god only knows”
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.69,0:01:12.84,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}"一個只有神知道的嶄新的世界"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.91,0:01:15.74,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}I'll always be on your side
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.16,0:01:17.04,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\pos(424,440)\fs22}I know you're hurting inside
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.91,0:01:15.74,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}我將永遠伴君左右
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.16,0:01:17.04,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\fs22}我明白你內心受到的傷害
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.74,0:01:18.94,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}To be a knight,to be a light for you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.74,0:01:18.94,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}做你的騎士 做你的明燈
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.94,0:01:20.38,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}We'll be shining bright
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.94,0:01:20.38,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}我們會無比閃耀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.38,0:01:20.93,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}No more tears
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.38,0:01:20.93,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}不再需要眼淚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.93,0:01:23.04,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}No more tears,everything works out
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.93,0:01:23.04,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}不再需要眼淚 我們將不再懼怕任何事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.04,0:01:25.57,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}That's "God Only Knows"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.04,0:01:25.57,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}那就是所謂的“只有神知道”
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.57,0:01:27.64,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Don't get me wrong
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.64,0:01:30.03,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}This is not real love but
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.57,0:01:27.64,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}不要誤會
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.64,0:01:30.03,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}這不是現實中的愛情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.03,0:01:32.74,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}I'll do anything for you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.03,0:01:32.74,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}但我會為你做到一切
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.74,0:01:35.86,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Whatever happens in my life,turn the page and come of age
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.74,0:01:35.86,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}不管人生將會發生什麼 我都將翻過此頁跨上成人的階梯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.35,0:01:38.57,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\pos(424,441)\fs22}Remember,no one can judge me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.35,0:01:38.57,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\pos(424,38)\fs22}記住 沒人可以批判我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.86,0:01:38.89,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Every end leads to a new beginning of the next stage
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.86,0:01:38.89,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}終結必將迎來新一幕的開始
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.09,0:01:41.69,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Try to make my life complete,trust myself
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.09,0:01:41.69,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}度過自己認可的人生 相信自己
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.69,0:01:44.32,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Be strong and do my best
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.69,0:01:44.32,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}變的堅強 竭盡所能
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.35,0:01:48.50,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Don't look back,carry on
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.35,0:01:48.50,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}不要回頭 繼續前進
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.50,0:01:51.80,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Be yourself…Be happy…It's your life…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.50,0:01:51.80,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}做你自己 要開心 因為這是你的人生
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.80,0:01:53.12,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}"God only knows"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.80,0:01:53.12,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}"只有神知道"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.12,0:01:57.21,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Find your love…Find your way…For your life…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.12,0:01:57.21,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}為你的人生尋找到愛與歸宿
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.93,0:21:54.77,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}恋じゃなくて愛よ あなたを想うだけで
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.93,0:21:54.77,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}不是戀情而是愛情哦 僅僅是想起你
